Power spectral & Alpha activation

Date: 03-Apr-2021 20:42:03

Power spectral & Alpha activation

Covid dataset: Controls subjects

  • Process description

Transformations applied to the data

Filtering the data at 0Hz and 50Hz.

Import channel info.

Selecting good segments from marks

Apply clean_rawdata() to reject bad channels and correct continuous data using Artifact Subspace Reconstruction (ASR).

Interpolate all the removed channels.
